title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 3' game
maintext:
TRENTON, N.J. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Thursday evening’s drawing of the New Jersey Lottery’s “Pick 3” game were:
2-7-9, Fireball: 7
(two, seven, nine; Fireball: seven)
